ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Onchain actions are transactions or operations that occur directly on a blockchain network, such as smart contract interactions, token transfers, or data storage. Our app simplifies the process of creating and executing these actions.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: How does your app simplify building onchain actions?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Our app provides an intuitive interface and pre-built templates for common onchain actions. It abstracts away complex blockchain interactions, allowing developers to focus on their core functionality without worrying about low-level blockchain details.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Do I need extensive blockchain knowledge to use this app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: While some basic understanding of blockchain concepts is helpful, our app is designed to be user-friendly for developers of all skill levels. We provide comprehensive documentation and support to guide you through the process of building onchain actions.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Which blockchain networks does your app support?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Our app currently supports major blockchain networks including Ethereum, Binance Smart Chain, and Polygon. We're constantly working on expanding our network compatibility to provide more options for our users.

FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about building onchain actions
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Onchain actions are transactions or operations that are executed and recorded directly on a blockchain network. They can include token transfers, smart contract interactions, or any other blockchain-based activity.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How does your app simplify building onchain actions?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Our app provides an intuitive interface and pre-built templates to help developers easily create, test, and deploy onchain actions without needing to write complex code from scratch.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: We currently support major networks such as Ethereum, Binance Smart Chain, and Polygon. We're constantly working on adding more networks to expand our offering.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Do I need to be an experienced blockchain developer to use this app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: While some blockchain knowledge is helpful, our app is designed to be user-friendly for developers of all skill levels. We provide comprehensive documentation and support to help you get started.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Is there a cost associated with using the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: We offer a free tier for developers to explore and build basic onchain actions. For more advanced features and higher usage limits, we have affordable subscription plans tailored to different needs.
